Precious.GumedePHOTO: supplied Sandile Shazi went missing on 10 September. Multimedia &nbsp; &nbsp; User Galleries &nbsp; &nbsp; News in Pictures Send us your pictures &nbsp; &nbsp; Send us your stories POLICE are asking the public to assist in a missing person case, which was opened in Hibberedene.Sandile Excellent Shazi (33), who lived at Sihlonyaneni location in Hibberdene, was reported missing by his family. Police spokesperson Lieutenant-Colonel Zandra Wiid said Shazi was reported last seen on 10 September. Shazi drives a white Toyota Corolla registration number, ND 775 827. Anyone with any information on Shazi can help the police find him by contacting Constable Lilly Shinga on 039 699 9824 or 083 240 6703, said Wiid. - Supplied.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.